e frying pan over medium-high heat and add butter. Once melted, working in batches, fry spaetzle for 2-3 minutes, until slightly coloured. Transfer onto a serving plate and garnish with chives to serve (see Tips)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["For ease, use a lightweight chopping board, preferably with a handle.","Spaetzle is a traditional German egg noodle. Serve it with stews, in soups or with a savoury sauce of choice (such as a cheese or mushroom sauce)."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","35m","4 portions"]}